sentences: Vladimír Guma Kulhánek (born 4 September 1944 in Prague, Protectorate of Bohemia and Moravia; now Czech Republic) is a Czech rock bass guitarist.

Vladimír Guma Kulhánek (born 4 September 1944 in Prague, Protectorate of Bohemia and Moravia; now Czech Republic) is a Czech rock bass guitarist. He studied at Institute of Chemical Technology in Prague.
